    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196040/extras/12005ee97017001b8668b10737b1418b.avif?t=1730791617\" width=539 height=82 /></span>.<br><br>Airborne Justice offers an old-school arcade experience for one or two players. As the Thunderflash team, Rock and Stan (protagonists previously seen in Thunderflash and Biomech Hell), you'll pilot a helicopter capable of rapid fire, maneuver through the clouds, and harness the incredible power of thunder. <br>Five levels filled with challenges create a short but satisfying game, with the option to replay with extra modes!<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A tribute to the 194X series and many other genre classics!<br></li><li>Play with a friend and enjoy double the fun!<br></li><li>Pixel art graphics!<br></li><li>Top-notch soundtrack!<br></li><li>Unlock incredible pixel art artwork!<br></li><li>Various power-ups and the ability to activate the &quot;Thunderflash&quot; bomb!<br></li><li>Secret extra modes: Speed Mode, Remix Mode, and Survival Mode!<br></li><li>Take down huge bosses by hitting their weak points!<br></li><li>Plenty of achievements!</li></ul>",
